, 2012"></div> /* */<span class="meta-category" title="Category"> <i class="icon-tag"></i> <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/archives/category/recensioni/" >Opera</a> </span> <span class="meta-author" title="Author"> <i class="icon-user"></i> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/ilaria-grippaudo/" title="View all posts by Ilaria Grippaudo" rel="author">Ilaria Grippaudo</a></span> </span> <span class="meta-tags" title="Tags"> <i class="icon-tags"></i> <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/alberto-mastromarino/" rel="tag">Alberto Mastromarino</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/andrea-cigni/" rel="tag">andrea cigni</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/beni-montresor/" rel="tag">Beni Montresor</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/daneila-dessi/" rel="tag">Daneila Dessì</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/giovanna-lanza/" rel="tag">Giovanna Lanza</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/madama-butterfly/" rel="tag">Madama Butterfly</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/marcello-mottadelli/" rel="tag">Marcello Mottadelli</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/massimiliano-chiarolla/" rel="tag">Massimiliano Chiarolla</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/opera-lirica/" rel="tag">Opera lirica</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/puccini/" rel="tag">puccini</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/roberto-aronica/" rel="tag">Roberto Aronica</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Alberto Mastromarino, andrea cigni, Beni Montresor, Daneila Dessì, Giovanna Lanza, Madama Butterfly, Marcello Mottadelli, Massimiliano Chiarolla, Opera lirica, puccini, Roberto Aronica"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/f56370b7da5e03bbc648642da149afc1" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/